des:
1470 & 100.3 WMBD is your news, traffic and severe weather leader for central Illinois. Greg and Dan weekday mornings and Markley and van Camp each afternoon.
Once enabled, just say: "Alexa, open w. m. b. d. radio" and Alexa will guide you from there!
